    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed or reviewed. Achieved levels are below required levels across all factors, consistent with a Not Accepted regulatory decision for MRL 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification completed. The assessment team notes that the rheological and boundary condition inputs used in the Monte Carlo analysis originate from the 2018 characterization campaign and have not been re-validated against the January 2026 model revision; however, the team judges this gap to be within acceptable bounds given the stability of the pump geometry. Package submitted for regulatory review.",
